  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/0a7949ff22f2622a08e7f9b5dd309be8.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>Life’s never boring with Cloudy and Stormy. This time our two pups got sucked into a video game due to a crazy coincidence! Luckily, they also gained superpowers which will aid them on this pawtastic adventure. Are you ready to help them get home and, more importantly, find their beloved blanket?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/88a90c3f9c1c0fe0b5c8322d3b227313.poster.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/88a90c3f9c1c0fe0b5c8322d3b227313.webm?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/88a90c3f9c1c0fe0b5c8322d3b227313.mp4?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/644236fccaf19356fec512b97cdeddac.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><i><strong>Travel the colorful world!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cloudy and Stormy, inquisitive as ever, are thrown into a new colorful world and they’ll visit every corner of it, from Crystal Caverns to a Castle in the Clouds. This land is full of obstacles and adventures! A singing forest? A jungle cruise? A dance-off with the bunny royalty? These are just some of them!  <br> <br><strong>Use Cloudy and Stormy's superpowers to easily overcome any adversity!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Cloudy ☁️ - turn into a fluffy cloud and fly high, glide on the wind, create rain that puts out flames and water plants!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Stormy <strong>⚡</strong> - lightning dash across wide chasms, open blocked passages, electrify the environment!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/f4cde2d8f67aa80b33d54270d5f791c6.poster.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/f4cde2d8f67aa80b33d54270d5f791c6.webm?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/f4cde2d8f67aa80b33d54270d5f791c6.mp4?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/63f4302ad4f1e9a06f3d91650c97aa98.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><i><strong>Help your new friends!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every adventure becomes a <i><strong>pawtastic</strong></i> adventure with friends by your side. Cloudy and Stormy meet a whole bunch of new companions on their way and won't hesitate to help every one of them. Captain Crab is looking for cooking assistants, penguin Snowball has a talent for getting lost, while kitty Luna is on the lookout for her runaway fish… and we haven't met everyone yet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/0158ff5102b91f5b8503b91257d6d47d.poster.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/0158ff5102b91f5b8503b91257d6d47d.webm?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/0158ff5102b91f5b8503b91257d6d47d.mp4?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/d6cd1af0d77b2ec179848460af3fdca5.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><i><strong>Collect... EVERYTHING?</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are not afraid of challenges you can use your superpowers to the maximum and explore every nook and cranny. Your efforts will be rewarded! Collect every coin, every crunchy snack, every costume, and even the entire soundtrack track by track! Use the treasures you find to decorate your hideout and express yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/4c4a50d7dda0ad0b021ab725206b8756.poster.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/4c4a50d7dda0ad0b021ab725206b8756.webm?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/4c4a50d7dda0ad0b021ab725206b8756.mp4?t=1762854940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352020/extras/ed6e3cf420ef7c7a6d32c3b60f9df023.avif?t=1762854940\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><i><strong>Game features:</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 episodes, each set in a unique colorful region!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 levels to complete!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 treasures and secrets to discover!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cast of charming creatures and travel companions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various minigames, cute pixel art, uplifting soundtrack & more! </p></li></ul>",
