e colorful region!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 levels to complete!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 treasures and secrets to discover!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cast of charming creatures and travel companions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various minigames, cute pixel art, uplifting soundtrack & more! </p></li></ul>",
